f=Product/price/operational/skill/price-skill-routing.md · h1:price Skill Routing Map=`new price / no WTP evidence ─► pricing-research (WTP by segment; value-anchored; flagged methods) \· │ WTP structure \· ▼ \· packaging-tiers (value metric; good/better/best; feature→tier; fences) \· │ structure` · h1:price Skill Routing Map=Non-leader: law (the Evidence Gate price runs monetization) routing decide WHICH skill WHEN. Handoffs out: loom (revenue experiments, registry) metric (revenue-per-user, churn instrumentation) board/precedent (locked-commitment changes, Fleet Charter Rail echo/comms (change communication) felix/Finance/future (margin/unit-economics boundary) spec (feature-to-tier seam) mia/Engineering (pricing-page build) anneal mispriced-and-missed outcome skill lesson). Precedence: research proposes, revenue experiments confirm; existing customers never silently repriced; locked commitments board; change logged proposal.